{
  "info": {
    "name": "getAttrService",
    "description": "Product specification retrieval microservice.\n\nBase URL: {{base_url}} (default: http://localhost:8000)\n\nSet the `base_url` variable in the collection or environment.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Liveness check. Returns {\"status\": \"ok\"} when the service is running."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Attribute",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "ASUS H610M-K — rear USB ports",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/attribute?name=H610M-K&brand=ASUS&category=motherboard&attribute=rear USB ports",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["attribute"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",      "value": "H610M-K" },
                { "key": "brand",     "value": "ASUS" },
                { "key": "category",  "value": "motherboard" },
                { "key": "attribute", "value": "rear USB ports" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Extract a single attribute for a product.\n\n**Product fields:**\n- `name` (required) — product model name\n- `brand` — manufacturer\n- `category` — product type (improves query building)\n- `article` — SKU / article number\n- `ean13` — EAN-13 barcode (highest-priority identifier)\n- `upc` — UPC barcode\n\n**Request options:**\n- `attribute` (required) — the spec to look up\n- `max_sources` — pages to fetch, default 5 (range 1–10)\n- `official_only` — restrict to manufacturer's official site, default false"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "ASUS H610M-K — RAM slots",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/attribute?name=H610M-K&brand=ASUS&category=motherboard&attribute=memory slots",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["attribute"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",      "value": "H610M-K" },
                { "key": "brand",     "value": "ASUS" },
                { "key": "category",  "value": "motherboard" },
                { "key": "attribute", "value": "memory slots" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2E GAMING G3424B — curvature radius (official only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/attribute?name=G3424B&brand=2E GAMING&category=monitor&article=2E-G3424B-01.UA&attribute=curvature radius&official_only=true",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["attribute"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",          "value": "G3424B" },
                { "key": "brand",         "value": "2E GAMING" },
                { "key": "category",      "value": "monitor" },
                { "key": "article",       "value": "2E-G3424B-01.UA" },
                { "key": "attribute",     "value": "curvature radius" },
                { "key": "official_only", "value": "true" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Restricts search to the manufacturer's official website.\n\n`official_only=true` triggers two extra steps:\n1. Resolve official domain via Ollama + SearxNG (e.g. `2egaming.com`)\n2. Filter all search results to that domain\n\nIf no official-site results are found, falls back to normal search and sets `official_only_fallback: true` in the response."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "By EAN-13 barcode",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/attribute?name=G3424B&brand=2E GAMING&ean13=4711081661634&attribute=refresh rate",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["attribute"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",      "value": "G3424B" },
                { "key": "brand",     "value": "2E GAMING" },
                { "key": "ean13",     "value": "4711081661634" },
                { "key": "attribute", "value": "refresh rate" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "When `ean13` or `upc` is provided it becomes the primary search identifier (highest precision), replacing brand+name in the first query."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Fewer sources (faster)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/attribute?name=H610M-K&brand=ASUS&attribute=TDP&max_sources=2",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["attribute"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",        "value": "H610M-K" },
                { "key": "brand",       "value": "ASUS" },
                { "key": "attribute",   "value": "TDP" },
                { "key": "max_sources", "value": "2" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "`max_sources=2` fetches only 2 pages instead of the default 5. Faster but lower coverage."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Specs",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "ASUS H610M-K — all specs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/specs?name=H610M-K&brand=ASUS&category=motherboard",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["specs"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",     "value": "H610M-K" },
                { "key": "brand",    "value": "ASUS" },
                { "key": "category", "value": "motherboard" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Extract all product specifications as structured groups.\n\nReturns a list of `groups`, each with a `name` (section heading from the page) and `specs` (list of `{name, value}` pairs).\n\nIf the page has no section headings, all specs land in a single `\"Specifications\"` group.\n\n**Extraction order:**\n1. httpx fetch of top 4 candidate URLs in parallel\n2. Pick the page with the best score (total_specs × 2 + groups × 3)\n3. If score < 20: Playwright headless Chromium re-fetches the top URL, clicks spec tabs/buttons, and re-extracts"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2E GAMING G3424B — all specs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/specs?name=G3424B&brand=2E GAMING&article=2E-G3424B-01.UA",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["specs"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",    "value": "G3424B" },
                { "key": "brand",   "value": "2E GAMING" },
                { "key": "article", "value": "2E-G3424B-01.UA" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "All specs — official site only",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/specs?name=H610M-K&brand=ASUS&official_only=true",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["specs"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "name",          "value": "H610M-K" },
                { "key": "brand",         "value": "ASUS" },
                { "key": "official_only", "value": "true" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Resolve (batch)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "2E monitor — typed batch (enum + unit + string)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/attributes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["attributes"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"product\": {\n    \"name\": \"G3424B\",\n    \"brand\": \"2E GAMING\",\n    \"category\": \"monitor\",\n    \"article\": \"2E-G3424B-01.UA\"\n  },\n  \"attributes\": [\n    { \"name\": \"Refresh rate\", \"type\": \"number\", \"unit\": \"Hz\", \"allowed_values\": [\"60\",\"120\",\"144\",\"165\",\"180\"] },\n    { \"name\": \"Response time\", \"type\": \"number\", \"unit\": \"ms\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Panel type\", \"type\": \"enum\", \"allowed_values\": [\"IPS\",\"VA\",\"TN\",\"OLED\"] },\n    { \"name\": \"Curvature\", \"type\": \"string\" }\n  ],\n  \"official_only\": false,\n  \"max_sources\": 5\n}"
            },
            "description": "Batch-resolve several typed attributes for one product in a single request.\n\nThe product pages are fetched/parsed once; each attribute is resolved against the shared content; then the AI layer coerces to `type`, converts to `unit`, and snaps to `allowed_values`.\n\nEach result returns `value`, `raw_value`, `unit`, `matched_allowed`, `confidence`, `source_url` (page the value came from), `status` (found|not_found|ambiguous), and `sources`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "ASUS motherboard — typed batch (one shared fetch)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/attributes",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["attributes"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"product\": {\n    \"name\": \"H610M-K\",\n    \"brand\": \"ASUS\",\n    \"category\": \"motherboard\"\n  },\n  \"attributes\": [\n    { \"name\": \"Memory slots\", \"type\": \"integer\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Max memory\", \"type\": \"number\", \"unit\": \"GB\" },\n    { \"name\": \"Form factor\", \"type\": \"string\" }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "description": "Several attributes of one product resolved from a single shared page fetch."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Debug",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "SearxNG search proxy",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/search?q=ASUS H610M-K specifications",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["search"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "q", "value": "ASUS H610M-K specifications" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Passes the query directly to SearxNG and returns the raw JSON response (results, infoboxes, answers). Useful for verifying that SearxNG is reachable and seeing what URLs it returns."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
